  },
  {
    icon: '📸',
    title: 'Handles Kitchen Photo Messages',
    text: "Facebook users message with photos of their current kitchen — cramped, dated, too small for the family. 'This is our kitchen — can you make it like the one in your gallery?' The AI acknowledges the photos, asks about dimensions and planning, and delivers the images alongside a structured lead."
  },
  {
    icon: '⚡',
    title: 'Captures Tagged Recommendations',
    text: "Happy extension clients tag your company when friends ask for builder recommendations on Facebook. The friend messages your page and the AI captures the enquiry within seconds — a warm referral lead with built-in trust and evidence of your work quality."
  },
  {
